1. Mount Local Code into the Container (Bind Mounts)
/path/to/local/code is your teammate's code folder.
/app is where your Flask app lives inside the image.

docker run -v /path/to/local/code:/app -p 5000:5000 my-flask-image


2. Rebuild the Image

docker build -t my-flask-image .
docker run -p 5000:5000 my-flask-image

